SUMMARY:Part Closure: MILDMAY LINE: Sunday 15 June\, no service between 
 Gospel Oak and Richmond / Shepherds Bush\, A special train service 
 operates between Stratford and Willesden Junction (Low Level) via all 
 stations to Camden Road\, then South Hampstead\, Kilburn High Road\, 
 Queens Park and Kensal Green. Use DISTRICT LINE services between 
 Gunnersbury\, Kew Gardens and Richmond and local London Buses routes 220 
 and 228 between Willesden Junction and Shepherds Bush. Replacement buses 
 operate.
